song.title: Endspurt
song.info:
My entry for the Oldskool Music competition at Revision 2015. Aimed for catchiness, following the "AHX pop style" from "Smooth Talker", but it also has a kind of "untz" factor to it (at least it did on the party speakers :)
Composed pretty much in a hurry during March/April. The final touches were done on the train from Frankfurt to Saarbr√ºcken and at Revision 2015..
